### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/user HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com"
}

###

### Retrieve a user by ID (replace `YOUR_USER_ID` with actual ID from the previous response)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/YOUR_USER_ID HTTP/1.1

###

### Update an existing user profile (replace `YOUR_USER_ID` with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/user/YOUR_USER_ID HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Updated"
}

###

### Remove a user profile (replace `YOUR_USER_ID` with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/user/YOUR_USER_ID HTTP/1.1

